{"tid":159682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"周浩鼎指判刑彰顯對暴力零容忍：隨時會死人","createTime":"2017-03-17T07:26:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-17T11:00:34.000Z","uid":48093,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"93cf40f93733d4af09357032ee7d19f099ed5bc3","tid":159682,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T07:26:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170317/large/1489733816_aa83.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170317%2Flarge%2F1489733816_aa83.jpg&h=499b066a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n旺角騷亂中首宗暴動案件，三被告被裁定罪成今被判入獄三年，民建聯議員周浩鼎認為判刑恰當，彰顯了香港法治及法庭對暴力零容忍；本身是法律學者的立法會議員梁美芬則認為，3年刑期並非很重，但相信對被告來說是沉重的教訓。<br />\n<br />\n周浩鼎指留意到法庭判詞強調因當日被告擲玻璃樽及鐵支，對執勤警員構成生命危險，「隨時會死人」，故認為判決合理，又指過去暴動罪較少出現，而今次則有足夠證據。<br />\n梁美芬則指，暴動罪最高刑罰是判監10年，現時判監3年，相信法庭已考慮到被告年輕及個別因素等。她又認為旺角騷亂的前身是違法佔中，許多人觸犯法例後無受懲罰，致有人以為犯法無嚴重影響，她相信法庭今次發出清楚訊息，危害公共秩序要負上刑事責任。"},{"pid":"3fe3665aa1362f53568d02301f2c9c7487a0a663","tid":159682,"uid":41969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T07:27:16.000Z","msg":"圍毆唔會死人"},{"pid":"db8218342dc3b7eca0855456f0e166079fe1d70a","tid":159682,"uid":9899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T07:27:48.000Z","msg":"佢思覺失調呀"},{"pid":"887a692a2a1624e744ab694eaf27253e38dd76b3","tid":159682,"uid":18241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T07:36:30.000Z","msg":"講緊七警案?"},{"pid":"2251cfd34390e306643c5fa533393cd0720c1ec2","tid":159682,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T07:40:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講緊七警案?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a0dbda7168606ec70d30e0e64594c78f1764d2e","tid":159682,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T10:35:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講緊七警案?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a53aad190bd28bcaf1e0b2f6dc2af0d46e19c60b","tid":159682,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T10:59:09.000Z","msg":"124"},{"pid":"1dde1ece3865d5e4dec38d5670a19b605d2d7413","tid":159682,"uid":19501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T11:00:34.000Z","msg":"又警棍又拳打腳踢，的確會死人"}]}